narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Any basic skill required for doing psychology research

I really gained an in-depth view into formatting. How to do psychology presentations and creating a manageable timeline for research. This course also increased my comfort conducting complex data analysis and incorporating it into my research.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: One of the biggest strengths of this course is the timeline it sets for students. I will definitely be trying to replicate the research parts/timeline with future projects and papers.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This is a requirement for psychology majors, and would only be helpful if you plan to do research in psychology or a similar field.
Yes! I really wish I had taken this course early on before other psychology courses. It has really helped with my writing, how I understand research, and my comfort with data analysis.
